>>> #witheyeheight
### `withEyeHeight`
<<<

>>> #witheyeheight-description
```js
dimensions.withEyeHeight(eyeHeight)
```

Creates new entity dimensions object with eye height specified.

**Parameters**
- `[js]eyeHeight`: The eye height.

**Return value**
A new `[java]EntityDimensions` object with eye height changed.
